Now, let's modify the aspect by adding a new advice method. We won't need to restart the application for the changes to take effect.

```java
// src/main/java/com/example/HotPluggableAopApplication.java

// ...

@Before("loggableMethods(joinPoint)")
public void logExecutionTime(JoinPoint joinPoint) throws Throwable {
    long start = System.currentTimeMillis();
    logger.debug("Executing method {} with arguments {}", joinPoint.getSignature().getName(), joinPoint.getArgs());
    logger.debug("Elapsed time: {}", System.currentTimeMillis() - start);
    joinPoint.proceed();
}

@After("loggableMethods(joinPoint)")
public void logReturnValue(JoinPoint joinPoint, Object result) throws Throwable {
    logger.debug("Return value: {}", result);
}
```

